posting_body: ['WELCOME TO LIFE AT SpringfieldThis beautiful community is conveniently located in Renton, WA.', 'Enjoy this quiet neighborhood close to shopping, dining, parks and schools.', 'Less than 20 miles from both Seattle and Tacoma, the propertys great location offers easy access to freeways and major bus lines.', 'Our one- and two-bedroom open floor plans feature upgraded interiors with faux wood flooring, fireplace, washer/dryer, and a private deck or terrace.', 'Enjoy all the amenities the community has to offer including a clubhouse, game room and fitness center.', 'A convenient location, park-like setting, and great amenities make Springfield Apartments the perfect place to live.', 'Find out more and let us help you find your new home!', '-Pet Friendly', '-24-Hour Service Line', '-On Bus Line', '-Clubhouse', '-Breakfast Bar', '-Game Room', '-Fitness Center', '-Full Size Washer/Dryer', '-Faux Wood Flooring', '-Wood-burning Fireplace', '-Covered Parking', '-Private Patio/Terrace With Storage', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
